  "text": "Skip to content\nHome\nATMP-Courier\nATMP-Core\nCustomer Order\nDriver Access\nLeadership\nPress\nContact Us\nBegin the Experience\nSECURE. TRANSPARENT. ALWAYS.\nEvery Delivery Executed with Absolute Reliability\nEvery order is managed with precision, transparency, and professionalism, giving you confidence and control over your delivery operations.\nGet Started\nLearn More\niOS - Driver\niOS - Customer\nAndroid - Driver\nAndroid - Customer\nFrom Pickup to Perfect Delivery\nPlace Your\nOrder\n\nSubmit delivery details quickly through our platform for seamless scheduling.\n\nDriver Assigned Instantly\n\nOur system efficiently matches the right driver to your package.\n\nReal-Time\nTracking\n\nMonitor your delivery from pickup to drop-off with complete visibility.\n\nConfirmed Successful Delivery\n\nReceive proof of delivery and peace of mind, every single time.\n\nPlace Your\nOrder\n\nSubmit delivery details quickly through our platform for seamless scheduling.\n\nDriver Assigned Instantly\n\nOur system efficiently matches the right driver to your package.\n\nReal-Time\nTracking\n\nMonitor your delivery from pickup to drop-off with complete visibility.\n\nConfirmed Successful Delivery\n\nReceive proof of delivery and peace of mind, every single time.\n\nPlace Your\nOrder\n\nSubmit delivery details quickly through our platform for seamless scheduling.\n\nDriver Assigned Instantly\n\nOur system efficiently matches the right driver to your package.\n\nReal-Time\nTracking\n\nMonitor your delivery from pickup to drop-off with complete visibility.\n\nConfirmed Successful Delivery\n\nReceive proof of delivery and peace of mind, every single time.\n\nCUSTOMER\nDelivery With Complete Accountability\n\nOur platform coordinates drivers, pickups, and drop-offs, simplifying delivery operations for businesses across multiple markets.\n\nLaunch Customer Order Portal\n\nWe streamline every stage of your delivery process by connecting shipments with qualified drivers, optimizing routes, and ensuring smooth operations for businesses in growing markets. Efficiency and visibility are built into every step.\n\nSaber Tech empowers businesses with disciplined execution, seamless delivery, and operational precision.\n\nAt Saber Tech, we redefine last-mile delivery by combining smart technology with disciplined, operator-led execution. Every shipment is carefully coordinated, connecting drivers, routes, and packages seamlessly, so businesses can scale without operational headaches. Our transparent approach ensures every handoff, pickup, and drop-off is meticulously managed, providing complete visibility and control.\n\nFrom multi-location retailers to fast-growing e-commerce brands, Saber Tech empowers companies to deliver efficiently, confidently, and consistently, turning complex logistics into a simple, reliable, and professional experience.\n\nRead More\nEvery Package, Perfectly Managed\n\nOur comprehensive services cover every stage of delivery, seamlessly connecting drivers, routes, and shipments. Businesses and individuals alike benefit from smart, reliable, and professionally managed solutions.\n\n1. Business Delivery\nFlexible last-mile solutions for small and mid-sized businesses, ensuring reliable pickups, on-time drop-offs, and complete operational visibility.\n2. Consumer Shipments\nEfficient delivery for individuals, handling items carefully with real-time tracking and transparent handoffs for total peace of mind.\n3. E-commerce Support\nStreamlined delivery for online retailers, optimizing routes and coordination to ensure customers receive orders quickly and accurately.\n4. Multi-Market Coverage\nSeamlessly expand delivery operations across cities and regions, scaling without operational complexity or logistical headaches.\n5. Real-Time Tracking\nMonitor every shipment’s journey, from pickup to delivery, with complete transparency and instant updates at every stage.\n6. Professional Drivers\nCertified, trained drivers handle every package responsibly, ensuring safe, timely, and professional deliveries across all locations.\n7. Transparent Operations\nClear pricing, documented handoffs, and fair contractor rules guarantee smooth delivery management without hidden surprises.\n8. Platform-Powered Efficiency\nOur proprietary system intelligently coordinates drivers, orders, and routes, reducing errors and improving speed, accuracy, and customer satisfaction.\nRead More ABout All ATMP-Courier\nDRIVER\nDriver Access\nSign up or log in to the ATMP-Courier driver platform for seamless, efficient dispatch management.\nDriver Sign Up\nDriver Sign In\nDrivers use the platform via a Progressive Web App that enables real-time dispatch. With enforced acceptance windows and instant notifications, drivers can maximize productivity, reduce idle time, and ensure predictable, reliable operations.\nExpert Leaders, Shaping Smarter Delivery Solutions \nSaber Tech Executive Team\nMegan Patrick\nChief Executive Officer\n(907) 250-8765\nmpatrick@sabertechlogistics.com\nCory Rankin\nChief Operating Officer\ncrankin@sabertechlogistics.com\nHamza Bhatti\nChief Technology Officer\nView More\nTrusted Solutions, Every Mile\nTrust Saber Tech to handle every delivery with expertise and operational excellence.\nFacebook\n \nInstagram\nQuick Links\nATMP-Courier\nATMP-Core\nCustomer Order\nDriver Access\nLeadership\nPress\nContact\nSupport\nAbout\nCustomer Order Portal\nDriver App\nSaber Tech © 2026 • Built on ATMP-core • Owner and operator centric logistics platform.\nPrivacy Policy\nTerms & Conditions\nTranslate »",
